# CODEOWNERS — chief-architect approval gate for L0 / L1 governance artefacts.
#
# Authority: ADR-0068 (Layered 4+1 + Architecture Graph as Twin Sources of Truth)
#            CLAUDE.md Rule 33 (phase-released L0/L1 artefacts are read-only;
#            edits flow through docs/reviews/ proposals)
#            Phase 7 of the W1.x wave (2026-05-15)
#
# Pattern: required reviewers MUST approve before merge for files matching
# the pattern. The chief-architect placeholder team is referenced as
# `@chaosxingxc-orion/chief-architect`. When the actual GitHub team is
# created, the placeholder need not change — just add the team's members.
#
# Gate Rule 44 (frozen_doc_edit_path_compliance) provides the in-CI mirror
# of this convention: any modification to a freeze_id-tagged file requires
# an accompanying docs/reviews/*.md proposal in the same commit naming the
# file under affects_artefact:.

# Layer-0 governance corpus (root)
/CLAUDE.md                                             @chaosxingxc-orion/chief-architect
